::Zardus::

Zardus' wrist comp alerts him of Unitron entering the lab, the Alliance 
commander's internal computer sending a responce.

"Please put the bot on the table and strap him in. Load program 2345a and run 
it on him. It will take care of itself," his internal comp says to Unitron, 
Zardus' lips not moving.
